{"tid":2306541,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台驚爆兩膠桶溶屍案拘八人","createTime":"2020-11-30T13:28:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T17:17:39.000Z","uid":98659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9c213306b44f4ef6494fcc05f9ed4e84687e8b09","tid":2306541,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T13:28:46.000Z","msg":"台中與苗栗昨日驚爆兩宗恐怖膠桶溶屍案，死者為16歲失蹤少女及54歲男子，兩案均由巨額金錢糾紛引起，由同一集團所為。一名集團成員因受不了良心譴責而自首，全案因而曝光，警方已逮捕集團老大等八名涉案者，不排除還有其他共犯在逃。據報，落網集團首腦10多年前因組建強盜集團判刑入獄，在獄中參加課程得第一名獲假釋，假釋期間卻犯下凶案。<br />\n<br />\n警方日前根據情報，分別在苗栗山區、台中民宅挖出藏着死者遺駭的膠桶。屍體由於被淋上強酸、灌入水泥，均已面目全非，只剩皮膚、骨頭與一點點肉，行兇手法相當兇殘。黃男埋屍地點曝光後，附近民眾感到十分驚訝，曾燃燒冥紙祭靈。警方正在比對DNA確認死者身份及進一步調查殺害或凌虐過程。<br />\n<br />\n均由金錢糾紛引起<br />\n據了解，16歲失蹤少女是其中一名死者，生前是集團某成員的女友。集團老大徐男懷疑她偷走300萬元（新台幣，下同；約81萬港元），2017年在新竹持刀將她殺害兼棄屍，少女男友全程目睹殺人、運屍、裝桶及埋屍等過程，惟被嚇得不敢聲張。另一宗案件的受害人為54歲的黃姓男子。2019年6月徐男因一宗買賣土地糾紛，涉嫌詐騙貸款2,000萬元（約543萬港元），黃男打算到法院作供，證詞對徐男不利。徐男於是在台中某狗場將黃男活生生毒打至死，並再一次膠桶溶屍。屍體被運到苗栗山區埋藏。<br />\n<br />\n警方補充，落網集團首腦徐男2008年組成強盜集團，招攬青少年搶劫，也曾強迫他們強劫民宅練膽，集團分工明確，警方形容其仔細程度堪比國安。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201124/OMX4YGEHMVESPI7DPJC32A2DEI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201124%2FOMX4YGEHMVESPI7DPJC32A2DEI%2F&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=5372ab33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201124%2FOMX4YGEHMVESPI7DPJC32A2DEI%2F&h=d12aa04c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201124/OMX4YGEHMVESPI7DPJC32A2DEI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GwOkctRKIZM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGwOkctRKIZM&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=bdee8498\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GwOkctRKIZM</a>"},{"pid":"07765306bec0105cd53264799c6f5fccf8069039","tid":2306541,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T13:39:40.000Z","msg":"有睇breaking bed 就唔會比人發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8ddee4a0bd89ca28ed9666dfc2aa9d2dd1bd3c","tid":2306541,"uid":122885,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T13:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oEaaiTf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoEaaiTf.jpg&h=193052dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d92a5f7704d3f852ab395f5554f0db0c749f896","tid":2306541,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"07765306bec0105cd53264799c6f5fccf8069039","tid":2306541,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T13:39:40.000Z","msg":"有睇breaking bed 就唔會比人發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c94d1049ce41725bfee6d9854309363d30aa5d","tid":2306541,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:13:58.000Z","msg":"條女攞個桶係父母屋企成年<br />\n<br />\nCLS"},{"pid":"d16d5aee06240444b5667589f7aecc69fa5ea0e3","tid":2306541,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:22:17.000Z","msg":"Breaking bad"},{"pid":"c879cc2ee9171efdd2a0a95ce24caf9afb9683bd","tid":2306541,"uid":299372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T17:17:39.000Z","msg":"警方形容其仔細程度堪比國安。"}]}